1. How To change first letter of the word to uppercase ?
        Change first letter using "substring(0,1).toUpperCase()" function and concatenate with
        remaining string using substring(1,String.length()).

2. In finding duplicates, we have to compare each character with the all the elements. when doing this, we cant compare string with character.
    So, we can convert the single String to character using "Character.toString()" method.